{"tid":1004832,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣諗住唔結婚，攞哂啲錢去旅行算？","createTime":"2019-02-01T17:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T11:34:45.000Z","uid":10679,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"84fca1b921a4422d05d1e246208ef88272649882","tid":1004832,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T17:36:55.000Z","msg":"見到隔離post講緊結婚擺酒閒閒地都三四十萬，不如攞啲錢去旅行好過，幾廿萬可以環遊世界啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />窮人學咩結婚生仔 <br />\n<br />\n利申：普通打工仔，搵17k一個月，每年去完旅行都好似等於冇儲過錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c84e4414b331f4691e3e802ccf9fe7572599e0b","tid":1004832,"uid":51920,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T17:39:33.000Z","msg":"話你型?"},{"pid":"8e41203d872283aa9ded1319dd140fd7c9795522","tid":1004832,"uid":138981,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T17:45:11.000Z","msg":"冇興趣結婚擺酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但唔關錢事<br />\n純粹覺得同居已經差唔多冇乜分別 重有唔想搞啲無聊大龍鳳show"},{"pid":"8849cb95d01bb3072a7c8415c0d732a0d2461725","tid":1004832,"uid":35746,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T21:36:29.000Z","msg":"兩回事<br />\n你結婚可以唔拜酒<br />\n<br />\n冇女就冇女"},{"pid":"da04f9582a60647c30cf408fa325a60869e9111f","tid":1004832,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T22:58:13.000Z","msg":"拎首期去旅行就有<br />\nBetween<br />\n去完旅行一樣儲到<br />\n係儲得慢左姐"},{"pid":"fb5f9c982d5847a296360a8f761d395723e9358b","tid":1004832,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T23:01:23.000Z","msg":"結婚一樣可以旅行喎"},{"pid":"7cd7f7667b93fd00180a1f4bcf14c5b46a178932","tid":1004832,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8849cb95d01bb3072a7c8415c0d732a0d2461725","tid":1004832,"uid":35746,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T21:36:29.000Z","msg":"兩回事<br />\n你結婚可以唔拜酒<br />\n<br />\n